!  * Either the @a tag attribute or the @a implicit flag must be set.
!  *
!  * @param[out]      event       An empty event object.
!  * @param[in]       anchor      The mapping anchor or @c NULL.
!  * @param[in]       tag         The mapping tag or @c NULL.
